{"batch_number":16,"batch_size":24,"cases":[{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-001","input":"网络骗局已不是新事物了。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-001","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-002","input":"每天，黑客和其他网络罪犯都在寻找最容易的网上目标。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-002","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-003","input":"你认为自己不够有价值，不会成为网上掠食者的目标吗？","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-003","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-004","input":"不管是你的身份信息、你的银行账户信息，还是单纯的你的电子邮件里的内容，你的信息都是有价值的，网上罪犯也会尽其所能来获取它。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-004","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-005","input":"他们就仗着你不认为自己会是个目标呢。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-005","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-006","input":"是时候把你的盾牌举起了，开始防范自己不会成为网络罪行的受害人。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-006","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-007","input":"让我们以基本的网络卫生开始——最简单也是最具常理的办法来在线上保护自己。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-007","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-008","input":"一个密码并不足以保证你的网上安全。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-008","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-009","input":"通过设置第二层的身份验证，比如确认短信、用身份验证软件生成代码、脸部或指纹识别，或安全钥匙，你会给你的银行、电子邮件供应商，或者其他你所登录的网站，一层额外的安全保障。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-009","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-010","input":"多因素身份验证可以使你 99%更不会被黑客攻击或使自己的信息被盗！","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-010","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-011","input":"黑客们会试图利用软件的缺陷和弱点。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-011","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-012","input":"在你所有的设备上都更新系统软件，比如手机、平板电脑和笔记本电脑。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-012","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-013","input":"切记也要定期为你的应用查询更新——尤其是网页浏览器——在你所有的设备上。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-013","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-014","input":"直接打开你所有设备、应用、和操作系统的自动更新是最简单的办法了。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-014","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-015","input":"点击之前想一想。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-015","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-016","input":"超过 90%的成功的网络攻击开始于你在钓鱼邮件里点击了一个不熟悉的链接。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-016","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-017","input":"一个钓鱼骗局是当一个链接或网页看起来是合法的，但是其实只是一个把戏，为了要让你揭示你的密码、信用卡卡号，和其他敏感信息。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-017","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-018","input":"另外，钓鱼邮件也可能试图骗你运行恶意软件，也被称为恶意程序。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-018","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-019","input":"如果你不认得一个链接，相信你的直觉，点击之前想一想。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-019","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-020","input":"一个强密码应该由 8 位或更多数位，并由字母、数字和特殊符号混合组成。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-020","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-021","input":"避免在不同账户上使用同一个密码。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-021","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-022","input":"理想上来说，个人也应当使用一个密码管理工具来生成或存储独特的密码。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-022","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-023","input":"我们的世界在不断地电子化，也在不断地联网，我们大家都有责任来真正保护我们都所依赖的电脑网络。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-023","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"},{"classification":{"confidence":null,"domain":null,"eligible":null,"notes":"","quality_flags":[],"risk":null,"script":null},"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1/sentence-024","input":"做网络安全的冠军，分享这些窍门给你的朋友、家人和邻居。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.cisa.gov/sites/default/files/publications/CHINESE-Simplified_4_Things_You_Can_Do_To_Keep_Yourself_Cyber_Safe_508c.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-024","split":"guide"},"source_id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1"}],"converter_output_used":false,"dataset":"blind-v2","generated_date":"2026-07-24","input_only":true,"name":"blind-v2-source-classification-batch-016","seed":20260719,"selection_policy":"all-source-cases-sorted-v1","source_snapshots":[{"id":"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1","path":"benchmarks/accuracy/external/cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1.json","sha256":"1ed350d426b370927d88e3f7310fad5d823507b9a214bc625dc2e5b12a0aa5bd"}],"stats":{"by_source":{"cisa-cyber-hygiene-zh-hans-v1":24},"total":24},"status":"needs_codex_first_pass","version":1}
